ZH: 我妈妈是一位主妇，她负责照顾家里的一切。
EN: My mother is a housewife, she takes care of everything at home.

ZH: 她是一名全职主妇，不做外面的工作。
EN: She is a full-time housewife and doesn't work outside.

ZH: 她每天都忙于做家务，真是一位辛勤的主妇。
EN: She is busy doing housework every day, she is a hardworking housewife.

ZH: 主妇们经常交流家庭管理的经验。
EN: Housewives often share their experiences in managing their households.

ZH: 她是一名教师，同时也是一位主妇。
EN: She is a teacher and also a housewife.

ZH: 主妇们要做饭、打扫卫生、洗衣服等。 
EN: Housewives have to cook, clean, and do laundry, etc.

ZH: 她是一名忙碌的主妇，每天都有很多事情要做。
EN: She is a busy housewife, there are many things to do every day.

ZH: 邻居们都羡慕她是一位全职主妇，可以陪伴孩子们成长。
EN: The neighbors envy her being a full-time housewife, being able to accompany the children's growth.

ZH: 她是一位有能力的主妇，能够有效地管理家庭。
EN: She is a capable housewife who can manage the household efficiently.

ZH: 她每天早上会买菜回来，做一顿美味的饭菜。
EN: Every morning, she buys groceries and cooks a delicious meal.

ZH: 主妇们也需要自我调节，保持良好的心态。
EN: Housewives also need to regulate themselves and maintain a positive mindset.

ZH: 她是一位有组织能力的主妇，把家里打理得井井有条。
EN: She is an organized housewife who keeps the house in order.

ZH: 主妇们经常参加烹饪班学习新的菜谱。
EN: Housewives often attend cooking classes to learn new recipes.

ZH: 她每天都很晚才能休息，作为一名主妇真是辛苦。
EN: She can only rest late every day, being a housewife is really tough.

ZH: 她是一位有爱心的主妇，经常为邻居们做些好吃的东西。
EN: She is a compassionate housewife who often prepares delicious food for her neighbors.

ZH: 主妇们是家庭的支柱，她们为家人付出了很多。
EN: Housewives are the backbone of the family; they have made a lot of sacrifices for their families.

ZH: 她喜欢花时间布置家里，让家看起来更温馨。
EN: She enjoys spending time decorating the house to make it look more cozy.

ZH: 主妇们可以通过网络学习新的家务技能。
EN: Housewives can learn new household skills through the internet.

ZH: 她每天都会和小孩一起做手工活，是一位贴心的主妇。
EN: She does handicrafts with her children every day; she is a caring housewife.

ZH: 主妇们在家庭中扮演着重要的角色，为家人创造了和谐的生活环境。
EN: Housewives play an important role in the family, creating a harmonious living environment for their loved ones.
